notes:
Positives include results from the CDC. Total tested includes repeat testing on individuals. State lab numbers are as of 8 am, other lab numbers are as of 11:30 am. Commercial lab numbers are subject to change. 
As of April 20, Cumulative Hospitalized + ICU includes both confirmed and suspected cases.
On June 30, MA decreased the number of cumulative hospitalization, confirmed and probable deaths "due to ongoing data cleaning which identifies and removes duplicate reports."
